snippet.title: Aquarium Travels Videogame Devlog 01
snippet.description:
Aquarium Travels - DEVLOG 01

Hello I am proud to present the first devlog of the videogame I am developing, in this session I show the design of a special level for the game, try to summarize the process in a basic way so that it can be understood as best as possible. Please like, share and comment.

Prev. Version Gameplay:
